overview: If you have been injured due to the negligence or wrongdoing of someone else, we are here to help you. At Ward & Barnes, we work exclusively for injury victims. We are Pensacola lawyers that have grown up and lived in this area since childhood. Because this is our home, we are dedicated to making Northwest Florida a better and safer place for its residents. We handle each case with aggressiveness and passion because you the clients are our friends and neighbors. Our offices are located at 2009 North Ninth Avenue in Pensacola.
